{
  "texts": [
    "Another major issue identified is the transfer of bias and tone from Internet sources to the generated article, with 7 out of 10 editors mentioning that the STORM-generated articles sound \"emotional\" or \"unneutral\".",
    "More analysis is discussed in Appendix E. This feedback suggests that reducing the retrieval bias in the pre-writing stage is a worthwhile direction for future work.",
    "Generated articles are a good starting point.",
    "As shown in Figure 3, editors are unanimous in agreeing that STORM can aid them in their pre-writing stage.",
    "It is gratifying to know that the tool is helpful to experienced editors."
  ]
}